  2021,"04",/general-conference/2021/04/21oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,6,Those in favor may manifest it.
  2021,"04",/general-conference/2021/04/21oaks,President Dallin H. Oaks,7,"Those opposed, if any, may manifest it."
